				<wikidot:authorName>Napo97</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3428089</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I haven't read that many SCP's, but for what I've seen this is really original. Loved it from the start!<br /> I also like the way it turns a little dark at the end. I'll be thinking of this when i get out of my room later.</p> <blockquote> <p>Subjects return from SCP-3562-2 approximately one hour after displacement</p> </blockquote> <p>I feel like here it could more specific about the subject's return, like do they just walk out the same doorway? How do other people see this event from our reality?</p> <p>Overall, could be a little longer, but you definitely have my upvote!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
